---
description: General project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

This is a thesis web application for reporting public lighting faults.

Do not use code from previous student projects.

The system is not a full local fault lifecycle management system.
It is a map and integration layer for DPMK/AUSEMIO.

Keep frontend, backend and database separated.

Do not store citizen personal data permanently.

Keep code simple, readable and ready for future development.
